function Input() {
  return (
   <form className="flex flex-col">
    <label for="" className="flex flex-col text-[14px] text-denim font-sans font-normal mb-6"> Name
      <input type="text" placeholder="e.g. Stephen King"/>
    </label>
    <label className="flex flex-col text-[14px] text-denim font-sans font-normal mb-6"> Email Address
      <input type="mail" placeholder="e.g. stephenking@lorem.com"/>
    </label>
    <label className="flex flex-col text-[14px] text-denim font-sans font-normal mb-6"> Phone Number
      <input type="number" placeholder="e.g. +1 234 567 890"/>
    </label>
   </form>
  )
}

export default Input
